{"tid":945452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(文化自信)  過聖誕節犯法？ 中國下令：禁放聖誕物品","createTime":"2018-12-18T01:49:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T01:17:00.000Z","uid":184679,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"d30a18ea80c758d918c982d5cf76685c9dba31b1","tid":945452,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T01:49:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181218/640_68593f486a097cdfd3edae6b14e7bae1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181218%2F640_68593f486a097cdfd3edae6b14e7bae1.jpg&h=d0e94659&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為了迎接即將到來的聖誕節，中國不少商場都開始擺出聖誕裝飾，節日氣氛漸濃。但地處京畿的河北省廊坊市近日卻發出通告，聲稱「為了維穩，執法人員要取締沿街擺放的聖誕樹、聖誕老人等聖誕節相關物品，同時嚴禁商店以聖誕節進行促銷活動，且23至25日期間，全市執法單位禁止休假」，引發不少中國網友不滿。<br />\n <br />\n通告內容指，為「切實做好聖誕節期間維護穩定工作」，「根據國家、省、市、工作安排部署」，執法人員要落實所有維穩工作，包括取締放在路邊的聖誕樹、聖誕老人等與聖誕節相關物品，嚴禁商家在櫥窗裝飾佈置、掛布條、放燈箱廣告慶祝聖誕，也禁止商家藉聖誕節舉辦促銷，同時執法人員要加強巡邏市內學校、公園廣場、商場街市、金融中心、商業街等，嚴查流動攤販販售聖誕節相關的商品。此外，當局要求全市執法單位於23至25日期間不得放假。<br />\n <br />\n通告曝光後，不少中國網友都質疑廊坊市當局的決定，批評當地政府：「有權力真是任性！」，有人則想問：「聖誕老人已經影響到穩定！」、「很懷疑政策制定者的智商！」。對於當局近年要求抵制西方節日，有網友感嘆：「為什麼？中秋、春節不都有活動麼？為什麼單單聖誕節就清查？」、「國外好像沒有這麼抵制春節甚麼的......」、「外國人春節去中國城逛一圈都能上新聞聯播哦！」、「過聖誕節不犯法吧......」<br />\n <br />\n中國自去年十九大後，開始「抵制西方節日」，嚴禁各地民眾慶祝聖誕節。不少小學校當時政策，開始宣傳：「勿忘八國聯軍之恥」、「向洋節說『不』，拒絕洋節，從我做起，傳承文明，過中國節」，呼籲學生們反聖誕，要慶祝的只有「毛爺爺的誕辰」（中共前最高領導人毛澤東的生日，12月26日）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181218/1485460/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181218%2F1485460%2F&d=LTtkzNEE4HXdLZFdqzpenTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=30dab017\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181218%2F1485460%2F&h=9dbe7aee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181218/1485460/</a>"},{"pid":"2fc92f16701563b4e62d81556953dcc375ecd98a","tid":945452,"uid":5218,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T02:01:07.000Z","msg":"搵人幫毛爺爺加頂聖誕帽扮聖誕老人咪過到骨囉。"},{"pid":"88da70b612e92cb9641a2d5add1cf6a58b3267d3","tid":945452,"uid":16676,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T02:04:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNmaKhG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNmaKhG.png&h=d20e7802&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n淘寶係咪死罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cde130150c3d84bae4ba81f88e4ee867f6485de","tid":945452,"uid":34377,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T02:06:30.000Z","msg":"唔過聖誕咪過農神祭囉"},{"pid":"2a682745e8e45f7a40ca3f5271c280f75869ee54","tid":945452,"uid":222727,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88da70b612e92cb9641a2d5add1cf6a58b3267d3","tid":945452,"uid":16676,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T02:04:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNmaKhG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNmaKhG.png&h=d20e7802&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n淘寶係咪死罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T02:06:49.000Z","msg":"簡直傷害緊十三億人民既感情"},{"pid":"b543ac528f1f7bd9c27291b7cf2238d83e929cb6","tid":945452,"uid":193893,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"2a682745e8e45f7a40ca3f5271c280f75869ee54","tid":945452,"uid":222727,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88da70b612e92cb9641a2d5add1cf6a58b3267d3","tid":945452,"uid":16676,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T02:04:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNmaKhG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNmaKhG.png&h=d20e7802&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n淘寶係咪死罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T02:06:49.000Z","msg":"簡直傷害緊十三億人民既感情"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T02:26:3